= SDL_LockAudioDevice =
Use this function to lock out the callback function for a specified device.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_LockAudioDevice(SDL_AudioDeviceID dev)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''dev'''
|the ID of the device to be locked
|}

